/>\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 渡輪擱淺唔使慌　乘客拍手讚船長"},{"pid":"046cc6336c8c05261b1ef98c4f5e000bc48f849a","tid":797136,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"又係時事台手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}